<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Gigi Hadid has welcomed her first child, a baby girl, with partner Zayn Malik.</p>

<p>The model's father Mohamed Hadid revealed the happy news after posting a tender poem for his granddaughter on Instagram Wednesday.</p>

<p>'Welcome my little grandchild. I wish for you the sun and the moon,' he shared in the note, which was titled: 'Grandpa's heart.'</p>

<p>Proud parents: Gigi Hadid has welcomed her first child, a baby girl, with partner Zayn Malik, together in 2016 above</p>

<p>'Hello little grandchild, it's me, my heart as happy as can be. I wish for you the sun and moon. I wish for you a happy time.'</p>

<p>'Know that Grandpa's always near, I'll do anything, anything for you my dear.'</p>

<p>'When I heard you were on the way, I smiled and wiped a tear away. I cried the tear because I know, my heart would always belong to you,' he finished before signing off. </p>

<p>Overjoyed: The model's father Mohamed Hadid revealed the happy news after posting a tender note for his granddaughter on Instagram Wednesday</p>

<p>Yesterday fans began wondering if Gigi and Zayn had welcomed their child after younger sister Bella Hadid, 23, posted a throwback photo with her pregnant sibling.</p>

<p>In the caption Bella shared a baby angel emoji and said:  'I love you both so freaking much -can’tstopcrying.'</p>

<p>Gigi seemed to hint that her child was on the way at the end of August when she shared a stunning photo of herself at 33-weeks.</p>

<p>At the time it was unclear whether she was counting down from the time of the post or the photoshoot.</p>

<p>Gigi confirmed her pregnancy in April, after 'family sources' first revealed the news.</p>

